mlock installation instructions
-------------------------------

mlock requires the libsodium release 0.5.0 and the OpenSSL libraries.

1. Basic installation
=====================

 1. tar xjvf mlock-x.x.tar.bz2
 2. cd mlock-x.x
 3. make
 4. make install (install binary and documentation files)
    (depending on your installation destination, you need to be root)
 5. make clean (optional)